README.html.title: Purpose | RisingV.GameData
README.html.summary: A gamedata project for integrating RisingV mods. Purpose Provide a maintained data pack for V Rising game data. Note that RisingV.GameData is used internally by RisingV.Core so this is not required as a seperate library mod if you've already installed RisingV.Core. Getting Started Prerequisites V Rising (vanilla game/dedicated server installed) BepInEx (version compatible with your V Rising installation) Build/Download Clone or download the latest RisingV.GameData.<version>.zip from the Releases. Deploy Extract the zip file to your /BepInEx directory. Development Install package: dotnet add package RisingV.GameData or Clone the Repository and Build: git clone https://github.com/RisingV-Mods/RisingV.GameData.git cd RisingV.GameData dotnet build RisingV.GameData.sln dotnet pack RisingV.GameData Add BepInEx dependency to your plugin: // Added to your plugin class [BepInDependency("RisingV.GameData")] Contributing PRs that add new functionality—or improve existing ones—are warmly welcomed. Please open an issue first if you plan a large refactor. See CONTRIBUTING.md for more information. Community Join the V Rising Mod Community Discord for modding support, updates, and discussions! License GNU GPL-3.0. See LICENSE for details.

index.html.title: Purpose | RisingV.GameData
index.html.summary: A gamedata project for integrating RisingV mods. Purpose Provide a maintained data pack for V Rising game data. Note that RisingV.GameData is used internally by RisingV.Core so this is not required as a seperate library mod if you've already installed RisingV.Core. Getting Started Prerequisites V Rising (vanilla game/dedicated server installed) BepInEx (version compatible with your V Rising installation) Build/Download Clone or download the latest RisingV.GameData.<version>.zip from the Releases. Deploy Extract the zip file to your /BepInEx directory. Development Install package: dotnet add package RisingV.GameData or Clone the Repository and Build: git clone https://github.com/RisingV-Mods/RisingV.GameData.git cd RisingV.GameData dotnet build RisingV.GameData.sln dotnet pack RisingV.GameData Add BepInEx dependency to your plugin: // Added to your plugin class [BepInDependency("RisingV.GameData")] Contributing PRs that add new functionality—or improve existing ones—are warmly welcomed. Please open an issue first if you plan a large refactor. See CONTRIBUTING.md for more information. Community Join the V Rising Mod Community Discord for modding support, updates, and discussions! License GNU GPL-3.0. See LICENSE for details.
